title: 244: MNF Recap; Will John Dorsey fix the Browns?
itunes:title: 244: MNF Recap; Will John Dorsey fix the Browns?
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks dive into the Dolphins' 27-20 win over the Patriots (1:04). The guys also break down the Browns hiring of John Dorsey and how he will retool their roster (7:33). DJ and Bucky then answer who the Eagles will turn to on offense (17:20) before they debate if OU's Baker Mayfield will be a successful NFL quarterback (21:18).
